dcterms:description: The meteorological data contains five indicators, which are the atmospheric pressure, maximum temperature, minimum temperature, relative humidity, and wind speed. The sequence of each indicator contains 500 elements representing the values of the indicator on 500 days.
dcterms:title: Meteorological Indicators

dcterms:description: The stock price data includes the opening price, maximum price, minimum price, closing price, and volume of a stock. The sequence data of each component of stock price contains 180 elements representing the price of 180 days.
dcterms:title: Stock Price

dcterms:description: The MC task contains 130 sentences, each with 3 or 4 words, categorized into food and information technology (IT). This is a binary classification task.
dcterms:title: Text Categorization (MC Task)
